JavaFX version -> 15.0.1

Create JavaFX global library on NetBeans:
-> Menu Tools -> Libraries
-> New Library with name JavaFX15
-> Add JAR/Folder
-> Search for folder javafx-sdk-15.0.1/lib
-> Add all jars inside that folder

Add new JavaFX15 global library to the project:
-> Right click on the project, select Properties
-> Select Libraries
-> On Compile tab, add JavaFX15 to Classpath
-> On Run tab add JavaFX15 to Modulepath
-> Select Run
-> On VM options write --add-modules javafx.controls

Done
